One night as I was leaving Zol's,
I heard what sounded like feet
on the Restaurant roof. I looked
up and saw nothing, so I went
on my way. As I passed the bank
I could have sworn I heard a
footstep on the roof. Once again,
I looked up to see nothing. As I
walked past the cliff, I knew I saw
something jump from the bank to
the cliff. I pulled out my axe, and
waited. Then as if out of nowhere,
I was hit from behind. When I
awoke, Dante and Shanki were
standing over me. They told me
I was now a member of their
family. Shanki had been the one
on the roof, distracting me while
Dante leaped from a bush and
bit me.
